<tr style="text-align:center;">
<th style="background: #efefef;" colspan="2">Agency overview</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Formed</b></td>
<td>June 19, 1934</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Preceding agency</b></td>
<td><a href="/wiki/Federal_Radio_Commission" title="Federal Radio Commission">Federal Radio Commission</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Agency executives</b></td>
<td><a href="/wiki/Michael_Copps" title="Michael Copps">Michael Copps</a>, Acting Chairman<br />
&#160;<br />
